<h2>1. Overview</h2>
<p><strong>Fominoo.com</strong> is committed to getting your fashion pieces delivered quickly, safely, and affordably — whether you're in New York, London, or Tokyo. This Shipping Policy outlines our processing times, shipping methods, rates, and delivery estimates for domestic (US) and international orders.</p>

<h2>2. Order Processing</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Orders are processed <strong>Monday through Friday</strong>, excluding US federal holidays.</li>
  <li>Most orders are processed within <strong>1–2 business days</strong> of receiving payment confirmation.</li>
  <li>Orders placed <strong>after 2:00 PM EST</strong> or on weekends/holidays will begin processing the next business day.</li>
  <li>During peak shopping seasons (Black Friday, holiday season, major sales), processing may take up to <strong>3–5 business days</strong>.</li>
  <li>You will receive a shipping confirmation email with a tracking number once your order has shipped.</li>
</ul>

<blockquote>
  <strong>Note:</strong> Processing time is separate from shipping transit time. Your total delivery window = Processing Time + Transit Time.
</blockquote>

<h2>3. Domestic Shipping (United States)</h2>
<table>
  <thead>
    <tr><th>Shipping Method</th><th>Estimated Transit Time</th><th>Cost</th></tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td>Standard Shipping</td><td>5–8 business days</td><td>$5.99 (Free on orders $75+)</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Expedited Shipping</td><td>2–3 business days</td><td>$14.99</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Overnight / Next Day</td><td>1 business day</td><td>$29.99</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Free Shipping</td><td>5–8 business days</td><td>Free on orders over $75</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<p>We ship to all 50 US states, including Alaska and Hawaii. P.O. Boxes are supported for Standard Shipping only. US Territories (Puerto Rico, Guam, US Virgin Islands) may have extended delivery times.</p>

<h2>4. International Shipping</h2>
<table>
  <thead>
    <tr><th>Region</th><th>Estimated Transit Time</th><th>Starting Cost</th></tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td>Canada</td><td>5–10 business days</td><td>$12.99</td></tr>
    <tr><td>United Kingdom</td><td>7–14 business days</td><td>$16.99</td></tr>
    <tr><td>European Union</td><td>7–14 business days</td><td>$16.99</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Australia &amp; New Zealand</td><td>10–18 business days</td><td>$19.99</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Middle East</td><td>10–18 business days</td><td>$22.99</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Asia Pacific</td><td>10–20 business days</td><td>$19.99</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Rest of World</td><td>14–25 business days</td><td>$24.99</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<p>Shipping costs are calculated at checkout based on your location, package weight, and selected shipping method. International shipping costs <strong>do not include</strong> customs duties or import taxes (see Section 6).</p>

<h2>5. Shipping Carriers</h2>
<p>We partner with trusted global carriers to ensure reliable delivery:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>United States:</strong> USPS, UPS, FedEx, DHL Express</li>
  <li><strong>International:</strong> DHL Express, FedEx International, USPS International Priority, local postal services (for economy shipping)</li>
</ul>
<p>The carrier used for your order depends on your shipping method selection, destination, and package size. You will receive your carrier and tracking information in your shipping confirmation email.</p>

<h2>6. Duties, Taxes &amp; Customs (International)</h2>
<p>International orders <strong>may be subject to customs duties, import taxes, and fees</strong> levied by the destination country's customs authority. These charges are the <strong>sole responsibility of the recipient</strong> and are <strong>not included</strong> in the order total or shipping fees charged by Fominoo.</p>
<ul>
  <li>Customs processing may cause delays beyond our stated delivery estimates.</li>
  <li>Fominoo is not responsible for delays due to customs clearance.</li>
  <li>If a package is refused or abandoned due to customs fees, the order is not eligible for a refund.</li>
  <li>We recommend contacting your local customs office for information about import regulations before ordering.</li>
</ul>

<h2>7. Order Tracking</h2>
<p>Once your order ships, you will receive a <strong>tracking number via email</strong>. You can track your order:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Through the link in your shipping confirmation email</li>
  <li>On the carrier's website directly using your tracking number</li>
  <li>Via your Fominoo account under "Order History"</li>
  <li>By visiting our <a href="/pages/track-order">Track My Order</a> page</li>
</ul>
<p>Please allow up to <strong>24–48 hours</strong> for tracking information to become active after receiving your shipping confirmation.</p>

<h2>8. Delivery Issues</h2>
<h3>8.1 Lost Packages</h3>
<p>If your tracking information shows your package was delivered but you have not received it:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Check around your delivery area (porch, mailbox, with neighbors).</li>
  <li>Check with other members of your household.</li>
  <li>Contact the carrier directly with your tracking number.</li>
  <li>If still unresolved after 3 business days, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@fominoo.com">support@fominoo.com</a>.</li>
</ol>
<p>We will file a claim with the carrier and either re-ship your order or issue a full refund if a loss is confirmed.</p>

<h3>8.2 Damaged Packages</h3>
<p>If your order arrives damaged, please <strong>photograph the packaging and the damaged item(s)</strong> immediately and contact us within <strong>48 hours of delivery</strong> at <a href="mailto:support@fominoo.com">support@fominoo.com</a>. We will arrange a replacement or full refund.</p>

<h3>8.3 Incorrect Shipping Address</h3>
<p>Please verify your shipping address carefully before placing your order. Fominoo is not responsible for packages delivered to an incorrect address provided by the customer. If you notice an error after placing your order, contact us <strong>immediately</strong> — we may be able to update the address if the order has not yet shipped.</p>

<h2>9. Shipping Restrictions</h2>
<p>We currently <strong>do not ship</strong> to the following locations: countries under US trade sanctions, North Korea, Iran, Cuba, Syria, Russia, Belarus. This list may be updated in accordance with applicable US export regulations.</p>

<h2>10. Holiday Shipping</h2>
<p>During major US and international holidays, order processing and delivery times may be extended. We recommend placing orders <strong>at least 2 weeks in advance</strong> for guaranteed delivery before major holidays. Special holiday cutoff dates will be announced on our website and via email.</p>

<h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
<blockquote>
  <strong>Fominoo Shipping Team</strong><br>
  Email: <a href="mailto:shipping@fominoo.com">shipping@fominoo.com</a><br>
  Hours: Monday – Friday, 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM EST<br>
  Response time: Within 1–2 business days
</blockquote>

</div>

